{"aitVersion":"3.2.4","fileVersion":5,"fileType":"test case","createDate":"2026-03-11T15:32:45.950Z","creator":"ajoost","dto":{"changeDate":"2026-02-23T09:59:33.563Z","creator":"vgeoffre","dbId":181,"released":false,"inspectionType":"FULL_AND_PARTIAL_TEST","revisionNr":0,"createDate":"2024-04-11T08:55:52.638Z","state":"ENABLED","testCaseId":159,"testSectionDTOList":[{"changeDate":"2026-02-23T09:59:33.563Z","descriptionGerman":"","dbId":8002,"released":false,"inspectionType":"FULL_AND_PARTIAL_TEST","createDate":"2024-04-11T09:00:24.290Z","state":"ENABLED","testElementDTOList":[],"title":"<!--(DescriptionHead)Target volume/lung mechanic change","titleType":"STANDARD","parameters":{"parameters":[],"rows":[]}},{"changeDate":"2026-02-23T09:59:33.563Z","descriptionGerman":"","dbId":8003,"released":false,"inspectionType":"FULL_AND_PARTIAL_TEST","createDate":"2024-04-11T09:00:24.290Z","state":"ENABLED","testElementDTOList":[{"changeDate":"2026-02-23T09:59:33.563Z","elementId":1001,"factor":0,"isOnReport":true,"dbId":31692,"createDate":"2024-04-11T09:00:24.290Z","state":"ENABLED","structureId":1000,"targetRawValue":"--><h4>Pressure Values: PEEP and Pcontrol</h4>\n<br>\n\nIn this test, the applied PEEP and Pcontrol are tested.\n<br>\n<strong>Note: </strong> For the testing of \"Pcontrol = maximum, PEEP = minimum\" the standart setings for I:E and \nRate are reduced to I:E = 1:1.4 and Rate = 12 to avoid auto-peep.\n<br>\nThe sequence for this test is:\n<br><br>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<strong>\n(ASL) -> (Setup) -> (Exec) -> (Evaluation) -> (CleanUp)\n</strong>\n</div>\n<br>\n<ul>\n\n    <li><strong>(ASL)-Block:</strong>       \n        Sets ASL resistance and compliance according to the product requirements.\n       </li>\n\n    <li><strong>(Setup)-Block:</strong>\n        Sets predefined values according to the product requirements.\n    </li>\n    \n    <li><strong>(Exec)-Block:</strong>\n        <ol>\n            <li>Starts ventilation</li>\n            <li>Waits for 20 seconds</li>\n        </ol>\n    </li>\n\n    <li><strong>(Evaluation)-Block:</strong>\n        <ol>\n            <li>Asserts PEEP measured by the ventilator</li>\n            <li>Asserts peak pressure measured by the ventilator</li>\n            <li>Asserts PEEP measured by the flow analyser</li>\n            <li>Asserts peak pressure measured by the flow analyser</li>\n        </ol>\n    </li>\n\n    <li><strong>(CleanUp)-Block:</strong>\n        Stops ventilation\n    </li>\n\n</ul>\n<br><br>\n<br><!--","targetTolerance":null,"typeId":1002,"targetSelection":null,"invertResult":false}],"title":"(DescriptionBody)","titleType":"STANDARD","parameters":{"parameters":[],"rows":[]}},{"changeDate":"2026-02-23T09:59:33.563Z","descriptionGerman":"<h1>Description</h1>\n<h2>Procedure</h2>\n<h3>What's been meassured?</h3>\n<h3>How is it asserted?</h3>\n<h2>Changes from original PPL:</h2>","dbId":8004,"released":false,"inspectionType":"FULL_AND_PARTIAL_TEST","createDate":"2024-04-11T09:00:24.290Z","state":"ENABLED","testElementDTOList":[],"title":"Pressure Values: Tidal value and PEEP-->","titleType":"STANDARD","parameters":{"parameters":[],"rows":[]}},{"changeDate":"2026-02-23T09:59:33.563Z","descriptionGerman":"","dbId":8006,"released":false,"inspectionType":"FULL_AND_PARTIAL_TEST","createDate":"2024-04-11T09:00:24.290Z","state":"ENABLED","testElementDTOList":[],"title":".........General Setup","titleType":"STANDARD","parameters":{"parameters":[],"rows":[]}},{"changeDate":"2026-02-23T09:59:33.563Z","descriptionGerman":"","dbId":8007,"released":false,"inspectionType":"FULL_AND_PARTIAL_TEST","createDate":"2024-04-11T09:00:24.290Z","state":"ENABLED","testElementDTOList":[{"changeDate":"2026-02-23T09:59:33.563Z","elementId":11010,"factor":0,"isOnReport":true,"dbId":31697,"createDate":"2024-04-11T09:00:24.290Z","state":"ENABLED","structureId":11000,"targetRawValue":"","targetRawValueTolerance":null,"timeoutInMs":120000,"typeId":11012,"targetSelection":null,"invertResult